transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello namaskar sir kaise ho aap?
Executive: Namaskar ji badhiya hu sab.
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Ek second do sir mujhe.
Customer: Bataye sir ji.
Executive: Kya batau samasya aati hai tabhi yaad karta hu aap logo ko. Sir ji mujhe phone kar lete fir se ticket open kar diya aapne.
Executive: Ticket kaha open kiya mai phone laga raha hu to switch off aa raha hai. Fir maine aapke personal number pe phone kiya hai.
Customer: Sir mera number to kaha switch off hai mai to isse abhi baat hi kar raha tha. Aap mujhe phone nahi nahi busy aa raha hoga kyuki mai call pe tha.
Executive: Pata nahi wo engage hi nahi.
Customer: Aur mera personal number sir discharge pada hai mera jo personal phone hai jaise ki abhi maine dekha.
Executive: Personal number pe hi to lagaya maine.
Customer: Sir aap ispe lagate na office wale number pe ye to chal raha tha.
Executive: Dusre number band pada hai abhi dusra number down pada hai pura.
Customer: Hello ek baat hai aap fir kahoge ki yaar aisi baat karte hai ye.
Executive: Hanji boliye sir kya ho gaya ab?
Customer: Ek to hota hai ek ek rupay dene wala aur ek pehle hi 100 rupay de de dono me antar hota hai na.
Executive: Kya hone wala?
Customer: Ek to pehle hi advance aapko 100 rupay de de ki aap mere ko sab do saal ke liye aap ye cheez mere mere ko de dena. Hmm. Aur ek mahine ke mahine aapko payment de raha maje lete hua.
Executive: Sir samajh me nahi aaya thoda specific karke batao mujhe.
Customer: Samajh me ye hai ke maine two year ka pack liya hai aur mera padosi hai wo monthly pack me maje le raha hai usko achi lead de rahe ho aap mere ko nahi de rahe ho aisa kyu?
Executive: Abhi uska naam bata do ek bar unka bhi account mai ek bar khol. Uska naam kya mai proof dunga aapke liye naam batane se matlab nahi hai. Ye lead ye lead monthly wale pack pe gayi hai lemon ki 500 pode ki. Mere ko abhi tak show nahi hai.
Customer: To mera fayda kya hua itna paisa kharch karne ka?
Executive: Hello. Ha kaha ki lead thi sir?
Customer: Ye Rajasthan ke Mandwa ki 500 pode lemon ki. Hmm. Ha ye uske paas chali gayi monthly pack wale ko TrustSeal wale ko nahi de rahe ho. Abhi tak show nahi hai.
Executive: To mai kya khaunga sir?
Customer: Ek second dijiye sir na mai ek bar bas mujhe ek second ka samay dijiye.
Executive: Nahi to TrustSeal wale ko verified customer kaha rahe jab acche acche customer to unke liye ja rahe hain jo monthly pack leke baithe hue hain.
Customer: Ek lead aapko kal dikhai thi red diamond gava plant ki. Hanji. Hanji?
Executive: Kal ek lead dikhai thi aapko soft lead aayi thi aapke paas kya kehte hai Rajgarh ki gava plant ki.
Customer: Dekho aap mere ko waha se divert mat karo.
Executive: Nahi nahi mai divert nahi kar raha hu. Meri baat suniye. Mai maine jo mera jo question hai wo uska answer dijiye aap. Hmm hmm. Aap divert mat karo kaunsi lead kab aayi usse matlab nahi hai mujhe. Mujhe ye hai ki ye lead mere ko nahi aayi.
Customer: [unintelligible]
Executive: Mai aapko proof de dunga screenshot hai mere paas. Ha aap screenshot bhej do sir mujhe.
Customer: Wo mere screenshot hai na. Wo bhej do to matlab kya hai mera mai two year ka aur three year ka pack lene se?
Executive: Sir ek bar aap mujhe screenshot to bhejo mere liye better rahega.
Customer: Screenshot aapke personal wale pe dal raha hu. Sir personal nahi isi number pe dal do aap.
Executive: Isse mai aapko aayi. Aayi dal do aap.
Customer: Dal do sir aap.
Customer: Ye dekho ye lead monthly pack wale ke liye gayi hai.
Customer: Mere profile pe ye show nahi ki hai kal se abhi tak nahi ki hai.
Executive: Ek second ruko.
Executive: Bas ek second ka samay do.
Executive: Ab aap online hai?
Executive: Dal do sir aap.
Executive: Ha sir senior ki call aa rahi hai ek bar na maine unko bataiye sari cheeze ek bar baat kar lo aap. Theek hai to aap kar rahe ho mai karu? Nahi nahi wo kar rahe hai call. Ek second dijiye bas mujhe. Aapko ek second me call kar rahe hai sir wo. Theek hai to mai kaatu? Ha sir aap kaat lo.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer is not getting leads.

- Feels monthly pack holders get better leads.

- Wants to know the benefit of a long-term pack.



Resolution:

- Executive asked for a screenshot of the lead.

- Customer sent the screenshot on WhatsApp.

- Executive said senior will call the customer.



Next Steps: 

- Senior executive will call the customer.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, subscription, monthly pack, trustseal
